            <title>[LU-13211] ldiskfs for 5.4.x post 5.4.6</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13211</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;A minor change landed in 5.4.7 stable that broke the ldiskfs build&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Update the&#160;ext4-data-in-dirent.patch to work before and after the change.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Linux commit v5.4.6-410-g6f63704838ff&lt;br/&gt;
ext4: check for directory entries too close to block end&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Adds a new &quot;EXT4_DIR_REC_LEN(1)&quot; usage.&lt;/p&gt;

